Package: badgecreatr
Title: Create badges for travis, projectstatus codecov and more
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: "Roel M. Hogervorst <hogervorst.rm@gmail.com> [cre, aut]"
Description: Tired of copy and pasting almost the same badges to
    every new project on github? This package will search and create badges
    in your readme.rmd file.
